of a mentoring programme. However, there are large differences between countries in terms of whether these 
programmes are offered only to teachers who are new to teaching, to teachers new to the school, or to all teachers. T A L I S Figure 2 @BULLET Access to formal and informal induction programmes Formal induction accessible for all new teachers to the school 
